reviews.text:
Interesting food ideas but obsessed with cheese.
Good try in egg Benedict, just need little bit more salt. Choosing sesame bun for bagel is wise, sesame gives a fresh smell and helps neutralising the heaviness of cheese, because cream cheese is just so overpowering the whole thing. Dessert named Stone, looks like an art piece, tasted as good as it looks. Coated with white chocolate, mousse filing is not too sweet and sponge cake adds texture to it. Served with matcha and coffee powder is adding another level of flavour.

YET I THINK I SAW A COCKROACH CRAWLING ON THE WALL.
Overall food = 4, cleanliness -1, food ideas +1, cheese obsession -1. Total = 3

非常用心製作的餐廳，老闆一人分飾多角，創出不同的新美食。非常有人情味的

Bagels必食～番茄香草大蝦意粉非常有驚喜！

甜品非常有特色～
小小鋪頭只得12座位， 只得老闆一人做曬所有工作 (包括樓面、水吧、大廚、洗碗及清潔), 老闆也很用心機烹調所有食物， 今晚試咗三文魚菠菜忌廉意粉 及 Ice Mocha, 下次要去試其他食物(例如Bagles)。
貝果不錯，如可非素食的全日早餐就更好了。
